mysql设置指定ip远程访问连接实例
1. 授权用户root使用密码rootpwd从任意主机连接到mysql服务器：
1
2
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'root'@'%' IDENTIFIED BY 'rootpwd' WITH GRANT OPTION;
flush privileges;
%指任意主机
2.授权用户root使用密码rootpwd从指定ip为61.139.22.32的主机连接到mysql服务器：
1
2
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'root'@'61.139.22.32' IDENTIFIED BY 'rootpwd' WITH GRANT OPTION;
flush privileges;
3.授权用户root使用密码rootpwd从指定ip段为61.139.22.%的主机连接到mysql服务器：
1
2
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'root'@'61.139.22.%' IDENTIFIED BY 'rootpwd' WITH GRANT OPTION;
flush privileges;
3.授权用户root使用密码rootpwd只能从本地的主机连接到mysql服务器：
1
2
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'root'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'rootpwd' WITH GRANT OPTION;
flush privileges;
以上命令在终端登录mysql后执行。



通过MySql查询某个字段存在于哪个表。
sql语句如下：
SELECT TABLE_SCHEMA,TABLE_NAME FROM information_schema.COLUMNS WHERE COLUMN_NAME = 'col1'
